== Description ==

The [[Image:Assembly_Import.svg‎‎|24px]] [[Assembly3_ImportFromSTEP|Import from STEP]] command opens a file browser window to search and select STEP files.

(STEP assemblies are imported into a single document.)

== Usage ==

# Press {{Button|[[Image:Assembly_Import.svg‎‎|16px]] [[Assembly3_ImportFromSTEP|Import from STEP]]}} to open a file browser window
